            <div class="article-main" data-spm="content">
                <article>
                    <section id="articleContent" class="article-content">
                        <div class="display-content">
                            <p>借钱的事情相信每个人都经历过</p> 
<p>俗话说有借有还再借不难</p> 
<p>一般对于借出去的钱</p> 
<p>最好的结果就是按时还钱</p> 
<p>但也有不能按时还钱的主</p> 
<p><img width="auto" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/67c57180a17d43d4bf3d083cc157fe2d.gif" class="content-image"></p> 
<p>比如下面这个真实的案例</p> 
<p>不久前</p> 
<p>一男子向熟人微信转账3000元</p> 
<p>对方承诺第二天归还</p> 
<p>可一晃大半年过去了……</p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/46866b6e3f854adc8963078bf563e8f9.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><strong>聊天记录全程高能↓↓↓</strong></p> 
<p><img width="558px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/f27b338ade1e4019ae50b980e955f732.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p>既然是给女儿看病</p> 
<p>那通融是应该的</p> 
<p>没关系没关系</p> 
<p>……</p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/e862eb1a79c8450b8dee6353635f4f4a.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/c6b61464105c4d02b09c654705118567.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p>打架斗殴被关了10天？</p> 
<p>很好</p> 
<p>又成功拖延了时间</p> 
<p><img width="558px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/fac48a8ad76744af856112d1bd776427.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/2495c219d9dc4529be2048b0ed5537bd.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p>转账截图放一波</p> 
<p>看嘛，正在处理中</p> 
<p>这一处理，又得一段时间</p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/49e24f532f114dd193f4af1bb0080159.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img width="558px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/0e6acf8380204e1781ad8dfa2b28231a.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img width="558px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/a69f6012ecaa428c9b9b37d92426cd71.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p>区区3000块而已</p> 
<p>还需惊动财务啊？</p> 
<p>3000块而已又不是3000万</p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/e6228dcff02c47a9a990a0caa7810d14.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p>账号被冻结了…</p> 
<p>不怪我，</p> 
<p>我也很被动（摊手jpg）</p> 
<p><img width="558px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/dfae22d64a1340688375c49440da1432.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p>这一晃4个月过去了</p> 
<p>前前后后被哄了15次</p> 
<p>到现在还没有还钱</p> 
<p><img width="558px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/6eb0d937e6384c75b4168e75c5385065.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img width="558px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/80a0769387e34074a47b986cec0caf2c.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img width="558px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/7e941e0ec32743428f1beaf5c8515b6d.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img width="558px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/50d4add0b9f042e78d4f362867f2e6a2.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/d63fb63e5c114fda9267268bfadeea8a.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/162413cd858c4eefa7cdb103b7665d5a.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img width="558px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/ba82bce7f6d340de82bb847ad4be3d7d.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/1ed15cae3b154c3c887b5b9b98a886ae.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p>毒誓都发了</p> 
<p>这下该还钱了吧？</p> 
<p>结果…</p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/6b6d8874fb894c3198e421d67ef0abe0.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/00a0b0bfa45640138ee7248c56fe5983.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/4c42cafa58344ee6a31195bb3f33add9.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p>时隔半年时间，催收确实没有效果，他实在找不到人诉苦，就在同学的微信群里说起了这事。</p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/ae40014ae0d247bf8997cac67f1e12e2.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p>后来聊天截图传到了朋友圈，借钱男子看到后称，“玩笑开得有点大，老弟。”并称两人聊天内容曝光，涉及到其个人隐私。</p> 
<p><img width="558px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/835e24d67e264e3c9029822f483651af.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/d3620f835a7947e19f0786c8c24d117d.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/3329dbb4d0b54de5ba138c2de461dd84.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p>最后</p> 
<p>竟然被对方<strong>拉黑了</strong></p> 
<p><strong>拉！黑！了！</strong></p> 
<p><img width="125px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/ab2e33f47a4f4a749bd2b7bf7e10833d.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/14c36dcf1e814e17aa67275999632d63.jpeg" class="content-image"></p> 
<p>来源：FM93交通之声（ID：hifm93）、成都商报、楚天都市报、网络等</p>
